.DT
add_item
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
add_item

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_item -  This method adds an item into the current list of gatherable items.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void add_item(string name,
string skill,
int diff,
int upper,
mixed extra,
string * season,
mixed quant,
string ob)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^name%^RESET%^ - the name of the item to add
%^BOLD%^skill%^RESET%^ - skill needed to find this item
%^BOLD%^diff%^RESET%^ - taskmaster difficulty
%^BOLD%^upper%^RESET%^ - taskmaster "upper" parameter
%^BOLD%^extra%^RESET%^ - taskmaster "extra" parameter
%^BOLD%^season%^RESET%^ - available season(s)
%^BOLD%^quant%^RESET%^ - quantity (int or function pointer returning an int)
%^BOLD%^ob%^RESET%^ - filename of object to be created
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/gathering.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method adds an item into the current list of gatherable items.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
query_item(), gather_item()

.EP

